name: Ai Mie (The Girl I Like Forgot Her Glasses)
description:
[NEW!] v4!

-You can summon her just using aimie, and she will come out with her default school uniform, you can use squinting tag to make her eyes squint, and use glasses to summon her glasses

v3

-carefully caption the training images to maximize quality.
-add squinting tag for making her squinting her eyes like when she don't wear glasses, use alongside glasses in the negative prompt.

v2
-Redone everything on ss_kohya instead of using A1111's Dreambooth -> LoRA Extract. Got a better result and better flexibility to change.

v1.1
-Reduce the model from 128dim to 8dim, greatly reduce the size of LoRA

Ai Mie from The Girl I Like Forgot Her Glasses

uses ai_mie, pink hair, medium hair to summon her, uses glasses to summon her glasses. put glasses to negative prompt to remove her glasses, Add sailor color, serafuku, school uniform, to summon her outfit, use squinting to squint her eyes, like in the manga.

I recently discover the manga and I like the dynamic of this couple, so I purchase a manga...and can't wait for an anime.
